#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:2
msgid "Cartography"
msgstr "Kartografija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:14
msgid "Align points to features"
msgstr "Poravnavanje tačaka prema objektima"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:16
msgid ""
"Calculates the rotation required to align point features with their nearest "
"feature from another reference layer. A new field is added to the output "
"layer which is filled with the angle (in degrees, clockwise) to the nearest "
"reference feature."
msgstr ""
"Izračunava rotaciju potrebnu da se tačkasti objekti poravnaju sa njima "
"najbližim objektom iz drugog referentnog sloja. U izlazni sloj dodaje se "
"novo polje koje se popunjava uglom (u stepenima, u smeru kazaljke na satu) "
"do najbližeg referentnog objekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:21
msgid ""
"Optionally, the output layer's symbology can be set to automatically use the"
" calculated rotation field to rotate marker symbols. If desired, a maximum "
"distance to use when aligning points can be set, to avoid aligning isolated "
"points to distant features."
msgstr ""
"Opciono se simbologija izlaznog sloja može podesiti da automatski koristi "
"izračunato polje rotacije za rotiranje simbola markera. Po želji se može "
"zadati najveće rastojanje koje se koristi pri poravnavanju tačaka, kako bi "
"se izbeglo poravnavanje izolovanih tačaka prema udaljenim objektima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:26
msgid ""
"This algorithm is designed for use cases like aligning building point "
"symbols to follow the nearest road direction."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam namenjen je slučajevima kao što je poravnavanje tačkastih "
"simbola zgrada prema pravcu najbližeg puta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:29
msgid ""
"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of point features"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| Omogućava :ref:`izmenu objekata na licu mesta "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` za tačkaste objekte"

