#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1193
msgid ""
"Extracts label information from a rendered map at a given extent and scale."
msgstr ""
"Izdvaja podatke o oznakama sa iscrtane karte pri zadatom obuhvatu i razmeri."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1195
msgid ""
"If a map theme is provided, the rendered map will match the visibility and "
"symbology of that theme. If left blank, all visible layers from the project "
"will be used. Extracted label information include: position (served as point"
" geometries), the associated layer name and feature ID, label text, rotation"
" (in degree, clockwise), multiline alignment, and font details."
msgstr ""
"Ako se zada tema karte, iscrtana karta odgovaraće vidljivosti i simbologiji "
"te teme. Ako se ostavi prazno, koriste se svi vidljivi slojevi iz projekta. "
"Izdvojeni podaci o oznakama obuhvataju: položaj (dat kao geometrije tačaka),"
" pridruženi naziv sloja i ID objekta, tekst oznake, rotaciju (u stepenima, u"
" smeru kazaljke na satu), poravnanje više redova i detalje o fontu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1203
msgid ""
"This algorithm drops existing primary keys or FID values and regenerates "
"them in output layers."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam uklanja postojeće primarne ključeve ili FID vrednosti i "
"ponovo ih generiše u izlaznim slojevima."

