"conflicting (thus unplaced) ones."
msgstr ""
"Zadajte da li se izdvajaju sve preklapajuće oznake, uključujući i one u "
"sukobu (dakle nepostavljene)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1247
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1291
msgid "**Extracted labels**"
msgstr "**Izdvojene oznake**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1251
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1362
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1576
msgid "Default: ``[Create temporary layer]``"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: ``[Create temporary layer]``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1252
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1363
msgid ""
"Specify the output vector layer for the extent(s). :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni vektorski sloj za obuhvate. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1270
msgid "**Map resolution (in DPI)**"
msgstr "**Rezolucija karte (u DPI)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1275
msgid "Default: 96.0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 96.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1294
msgid ""
"Point vector layer representing the fetched labels. Each feature has "
"attributes identifying its source (layer, feature ID) and the assigned "
"labeling properties (text, font, size, rotation, ...). A default style with "
"labeling and null symbol is also applied to the layer."
msgstr ""
"Tačkasti vektorski sloj koji predstavlja preuzete oznake. Svaki objekat ima "
"atribute koji identifikuju njegov izvor (sloj, ID objekta) i dodeljena "
"svojstva označavanja (tekst, font, veličina, rotacija, ...). Na sloj se "
"primenjuje i podrazumevani stil sa označavanjem i praznim simbolom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1299
msgid ""
"Because some of the generated fields have name with more than 10 characters,"
" using the ESRI shapefile format (:file:`.SHP`) to store the output may lead"
" to unexpected rendering while loading the layer in QGIS."
msgstr ""
"Pošto neka od generisanih polja imaju naziv duži od 10 znakova, korišćenje "
"ESRI shapefile formata (:file:`.SHP`) za čuvanje izlaza može dovesti do "
"neočekivanog iscrtavanja pri učitavanju sloja u QGIS."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1306
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:extractlabels``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:extractlabels``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1316
msgid "Print layout map extent to layer"
msgstr "Obuhvat karte rasporeda za štampu u sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1318
msgid ""
"Creates a polygon layer containing the extent of a print layout map item (or"
" items), with attributes specifying the map size (in layout units, i.e. the "
":ref:`reference map <reference_map>` units), scale and rotation."
msgstr ""
"Pravi poligonski sloj koji sadrži obuhvat stavke (ili stavki) karte u "
"rasporedu za štampu, sa atributima koji zadaju veličinu karte (u jedinicama "
"rasporeda, tj. jedinicama :ref:`referentne karte <reference_map>`), razmeru "
"i rotaciju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1322
msgid ""
"If the map item parameter is specified, then only the matching map extent "
"will be exported. If it is not specified, all map extents from the layout "
"will be exported."
msgstr ""
"Ako se zada parametar stavke karte, izvozi se samo odgovarajući obuhvat "
"karte. Ako se ne zada, izvoze se svi obuhvati karata iz rasporeda."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1325
msgid ""
"Optionally, a specific output CRS can be specified. If it is not specified, "
"the original map item CRS will be used."
msgstr ""
"Opciono se može zadati određeni izlazni CRS. Ako se ne zada, koristi se "
"originalni CRS stavke karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1346
msgid "A print layout in the current project"
msgstr "Raspored za štampu u tekućem projektu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1347
msgid "**Map item**"
msgstr "**Stavka karte**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1350
msgid "``MAP``"
msgstr "``MAP``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1353
msgid "Default: *All the map items*"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: *Sve stavke karte*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1354
msgid ""
"The map item(s) whose information you want to extract. If none is provided "
"then all the map items are processed."
msgstr ""
"Stavke karte čije podatke želite da izdvojite. Ako se nijedna ne zada, "
"obrađuju se sve stavke karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1358
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1407
msgid "**Extent**"
msgstr "**Obuhvat**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1360
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1409
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1527
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1574
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1597
msgid "[vector: polygon]"
msgstr "[vektor: poligon]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1381
msgid "**Override CRS**"
msgstr "**Zameni CRS**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1384
msgid "``CRS``"
msgstr "``CRS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1385
msgid "[crs]"
msgstr "[crs]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1387
msgid "Default: *The layout CRS*"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: *CRS rasporeda*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1388
msgid ""
"Select the CRS for the layer in which the information will be reported."
msgstr "Izaberite CRS sloja u kome će podaci biti prijavljeni."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1403
msgid "**Map height**"
msgstr "**Visina karte**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1404
msgid "``HEIGHT``"
msgstr "``HEIGHT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1410
msgid ""
"Output polygon vector layer containing extents of all the input layout map "
"item(s)"
msgstr ""
"Izlazni poligonski vektorski sloj koji sadrži obuhvate svih ulaznih stavki "
"karte iz rasporeda"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1412
msgid "**Map rotation**"
msgstr "**Rotacija karte**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1413
msgid "``ROTATION``"
msgstr "``ROTATION``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1420
msgid "**Map width**"
msgstr "**Širina karte**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1421
msgid "``WIDTH``"
msgstr "``WIDTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1428
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:printlayoutmapextenttolayer``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:printlayoutmapextenttolayer``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1438
msgid "Set layer style"
msgstr "Postavljanje stila sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1440
msgid ""
"Applies a provided style to a layer. The style must be defined in a "
":file:`QML` file."
msgstr ""
"Primenjuje zadati stil na sloj. Stil mora biti definisan u :file:`QML` "
"datoteci."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1443
msgid ""
"No new output are created: the style is immediately assigned to the layer."
msgstr "Ne kreiraju se novi izlazi: stil se odmah dodeljuje sloju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1457
msgid "**Input Layer**"
msgstr "**Ulazni sloj**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1459
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1651
msgid "[layer]"
msgstr "[sloj]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1460
msgid "Input layer you want to apply the style to"
msgstr "Ulazni sloj na koji želite da primenite stil"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1461
msgid "**Style file**"
msgstr "**Datoteka stila**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1464
msgid "Path to the ``.qml`` file of the style"
msgstr "Putanja do ``.qml`` datoteke stila"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1481
msgid "The input layer with the new style assigned. No new layer is created."
msgstr "Ulazni sloj sa dodeljenim novim stilom. Novi sloj se ne kreira."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1486
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:setlayerstyle``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:setlayerstyle``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1496
msgid "Topological coloring"
msgstr "Topološko bojenje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1497
msgid ""
"Assigns a color index to polygon features in such a way that no adjacent "
"polygons share the same color index, whilst minimizing the number of colors "
"required."
msgstr ""
"Dodeljuje indeks boje poligonskim objektima tako da nijedan susedni poligon "
"nema isti indeks boje, uz minimizovanje potrebnog broja boja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1500
msgid "The algorithm allows choice of method to use when assigning colors."
msgstr "Algoritam omogućava izbor metoda koji se koristi pri dodeli boja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1502
msgid ""
"A minimum number of colors can be specified if desired. The color index is "
"saved to a new attribute named **color_id**."
msgstr ""
"Po želji se može zadati najmanji broj boja. Indeks boje čuva se u novom "
"atributu pod nazivom **color_id**."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1505
msgid ""
"The following example shows the algorithm with four different colors chosen;"
" as you can see each color class has the same amount of features."
msgstr ""
"Sledeći primer prikazuje algoritam sa izabrane četiri različite boje; kao "
"što vidite, svaka klasa boje ima isti broj objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1511
msgid "Topological colors example"
msgstr "Primer topoloških boja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1528
msgid "The input polygon layer"
msgstr "Ulazni poligonski sloj"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1529
msgid "**Minimum number of colors**"
msgstr "**Najmanji broj boja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1530
msgid "``MIN_COLORS``"
msgstr "``MIN_COLORS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1533
msgid "Default: 4"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 4"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1534
msgid "The minimum number of colors to assign. Minimum 1, maximum 1000."
msgstr "Najmanji broj boja koje se dodeljuju. Minimum 1, maksimum 1000."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1536
msgid "**Minimum distance between features**"
msgstr "**Najmanje rastojanje između objekata**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1537
msgid "``MIN_DISTANCE``"
msgstr "``MIN_DISTANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1540
msgid "Default: 0.0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 0.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1541
msgid ""
"Prevent nearby (but non-touching) features from being assigned equal colors."
" Minimum 0.0."
msgstr ""
"Sprečava da bliski (ali nedodirujući) objekti dobiju iste boje. Minimum 0.0."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1544
msgid "**Balance color assignment**"
msgstr "**Uravnoteži dodelu boja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1545
msgid "``BALANCE``"
msgstr "``BALANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1549
msgid "Options are:"
msgstr "Opcije su:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1551
msgid "0 --- By feature count"
msgstr "0 --- Po broju objekata"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1553
msgid ""
"Attempts to assign colors so that the count of features assigned to each "
"individual color index is balanced."
msgstr ""
"Pokušava da dodeli boje tako da broj objekata dodeljenih svakom pojedinačnom"
" indeksu boje bude uravnotežen."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1557
msgid "1 --- By assigned area"
msgstr "1 --- Po dodeljenoj površini"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1559
msgid ""
"Assigns colors so that the total area of features assigned to each color is "
"balanced. This mode can be useful to help avoid large features resulting in "
"one of the colors appearing more dominant on a colored map."
msgstr ""
"Dodeljuje boje tako da ukupna površina objekata dodeljenih svakoj boji bude "
"uravnotežena. Ovaj režim može pomoći da veliki objekti ne učine jednu od "
"boja dominantnijom na obojenoj karti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1565
msgid "2 --- By distance between colors"
msgstr "2 --- Po rastojanju između boja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1567
msgid ""
"Assigns colors in order to maximize the distance between features of the "
"same color. This mode helps to create a more uniform distribution of colors "
"across a map."
msgstr ""
"Dodeljuje boje tako da se maksimizuje rastojanje između objekata iste boje. "
"Ovaj režim pomaže da raspodela boja po karti bude ravnomernija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1572
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1595
msgid "**Colored**"
msgstr "**Obojeno**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1577
msgid "Specify the output layer. :ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr "Zadajte izlazni sloj. :ref:`Jedno od <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1598
msgid "Polygon vector layer with an added ``color_id`` column"
msgstr "Poligonski vektorski sloj sa dodatom kolonom ``color_id``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1603
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:topologicalcoloring``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``qgis:topologicalcoloring``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1613
msgid "Transfer annotations from main layer"
msgstr "Prenos napomena iz glavnog sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1615
msgid ""
"Transfers all :ref:`annotations <annotation_layer>` from the main annotation"
" layer in a project to a new annotation layer. Items placement can then be "
"adjusted within the layer stack."
msgstr ""
"Prenosi sve :ref:`napomene <annotation_layer>` iz glavnog sloja napomena u "
"projektu u novi sloj napomena. Položaj stavki se zatim može podesiti unutar "
"niza slojeva."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1630
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1649
msgid "**New layer name**"
msgstr "**Naziv novog sloja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1631
msgid "``LAYER_NAME``"
msgstr "``LAYER_NAME``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1634
msgid "Default: 'Annotations'"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 'Annotations'"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1635
msgid "Name of the annotations layer to create"
msgstr "Naziv sloja napomena koji se kreira"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1652
msgid "A layer with items from the main annotation layer"
msgstr "Sloj sa stavkama iz glavnog sloja napomena"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/cartography.rst:1657
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:transferannotationsfrommain``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:transferannotationsfrommain``"
